      "post_id" : 2965803,
      "comment_id" : 3024822,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
      "body" : "+1 for the algorithm, though OP says that there&#39;s only 10 elements. And nice way of using the random numbers with <code>ArrayList</code>. Much simpler than my suggestion. I think it would result in reordering of the elements though."
