      "comment_id" : 110657671,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "When I use the suggested <code>List&lt;String&gt; list = new LinkedList(Arrays.asList(split));</code> how do I avoid the annoying lint warning &quot;<code>raw use of parameterised class LinkedList</code>&quot;... usually warnings are there for a reason so I&#39;d rather not just suppress it..."
